title: 1995 Kazakhstan Cup
text: The 1995 Kazakhstan Cup is the fourth season of the <a href="Kazakhstan%20Cup">Kazakhstan Cup</a>, the annual nationwide <a href="Association%20football">football</a> cup competition of <a href="Kazakhstan">Kazakhstan</a> since the independence of the country. The competition begins on 9 May 1995, and will end with the final in November 1995. <a href="FC%20Vostok">Vostok</a> are the defending champions, having won their first cup in the <a href="1994%20Kazakhstan%20Cup">1994 competition</a>.
